The '''Fell Winter''' of {{FA|495}}/[[First Age 496|496]] was especially long and bitter, with ice and snow from November to March.<ref name="WJ-WH">{{WJ|I}}, p. 256</ref> It came immediately after the [[Fall of Nargothrond]], hindering both [[Túrin|Túrin's]] journey to [[Dor-lómin]] and [[Tuor]] and [[Voronwë|Voronwë's]] to [[Gondolin]].<ref name="CH-RD">{{CH|12}}</ref><ref>{{GA|286}}</ref><ref name="UT-TG">{{UT|1}}</ref>

